# 🟣 **SECTION 4 — PRODUCTIVITY BOOSTERS**
### ⚡ Shortcuts • Tricks • Data Cleaning

---

# 💡 Tips & Shortcuts

**Shortcuts** <!-- .element: .fragment -->  
- Copy/Paste → <kbd>Ctrl</kbd>+<kbd>C</kbd>/<kbd>V</kbd> <!-- .element: .fragment -->
- Undo → <kbd>Ctrl</kbd>+<kbd>Z</kbd> <!-- .element: .fragment -->
- Select All → <kbd>Ctrl</kbd>+<kbd>A</kbd> <!-- .element: .fragment -->

**Speed Tricks**  
- AutoSum → <kbd>Alt</kbd>+<kbd>=</kbd> <!-- .element: .fragment -->
- Fill Series → Drag fill handle <!-- .element: .fragment -->
- Freeze Panes → View → Freeze Panes <!-- .element: .fragment -->
- Hide Columns → Right-click → Hide <!-- .element: .fragment -->

📷 *[Screenshot: Shortcut keys]*

---

# 🧹 Data Cleaning

**Step 1 — Remove Blank Rows** <!-- .element: .fragment -->  
- Filter → Blanks → Delete <!-- .element: .fragment -->

**Step 2 — Remove Duplicates**  
- Data → Remove Duplicates <!-- .element: .fragment -->

**Step 3 — Text to Columns**  
- Split by comma/space <!-- .element: .fragment -->

**Step 4 — Trim Spaces**  
- =TRIM(A1) <!-- .element: .fragment -->

📷 *[Screenshot: Remove Duplicates dialog]*

