# ⚠ Common Excel Mistakes

- Not saving often <!-- .element: .fragment -->
- Numbers stored as text <!-- .element: .fragment -->
- Not naming ranges <!-- .element: .fragment -->
- Forgetting $ in formulas <!-- .element: .fragment -->
- Overcomplicating formulas <!-- .element: .fragment -->

